# Force LF line endings for all text files. The site is deployed from this
# repo and contributors mix Linux/WSL/macOS/Windows; without this, every
# `git add` from a CRLF working tree emits a noisy warning per file.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Mark binary assets so git never tries to munge them.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.ico binary
